Blizzard,makers,of,the,popular,online,MMORPG,World,of,Warcraft,provide,this,API,for,users,who,are,interested,in,gathering,game,statistics,and,data,Users,can,gather,data,by,categories,such,as,realm,profile,item,arena,team,and,more,This,open,API,is,created,as,a,service,to,the,World,of,Warcraft,community,There,are,no,signup,requirements,or,fees,for,using,this,REST,based,API,Users,are,limited,to,requests,per,day,however,this,limit,can,be,exceeded,for,those,who,register,an,application,Applications,can,be,registered,at,api,support,blizzard,com